snippet.title: Terrene 2.0 (Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
Explore a universe by air and by foot.  Fight creepy alien bugs.  Discover labyrinths, loot and guns.  Mine for ores to aid you in your journey.
2.0 brings a new level of added features, systems and items.  Check it out now!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1472600/Terrene__An_Evidence_Of_Life_Game/

Discord: https://discord.gg/GV9unF3Sw3
